},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:13:50.000Z","msg":"特徵是甚麼？2個西？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:15:04.000Z","msg":"有鳩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:27:21.000Z","msg":"一條鳩，一塊閪，一個屎忽蕯嘅生化人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48551b3d8f916f00697178c64e4d06bcda0b3b2c","tid":2159294,"uid":70487,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:27:25.000Z","msg":"郭生大力擁護支共政權，<br />\n<br />\n不敢喊滅共，只想用&quot;聯邦&quot;名義取代習近平<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8cae4c5de4066214f172367cc8aec71b5b1ceba","tid":2159294,"uid":55493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:28:50.000Z","msg":"冇片講經咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a5a389fec7ccc5620e608975dce12b7177171a8","tid":2159294,"uid":1886,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:30:13.000Z","msg":"郭文貴：中共過埋2020年仲未收皮我就跳樓死！<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2661924\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2661924&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJCZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=88f85398\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2661924&h=4b21dc27\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2661924</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\"><span class=\"red\">2019-01-04 16:32:40</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/12/06/4kDjBt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F12%2F06%2F4kDjBt.png&h=2d3a0463&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</p><br />\n<br />\n一直預告西方世界將與中國全面對抗的郭文貴還強調：「<span class=\"red\"><strong>2020年是結束共產黨在中國的最後一年，否則文貴就從那18樓跳下去，大家要記住我的承諾。</strong></span>」<br />\n<br />\n郭文貴又爆料：中共將於今年6/4滅亡<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3071249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3071249&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJCZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=a4884f6f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3071249&h=2b44cc57\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3071249</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"small\">2020-02-18 01:35:08</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/02/18/phpkwmUEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F02%2F18%2FphpkwmUEi.jpg&h=81372548&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n<br />\n流亡美國的中國富商郭文貴不定時暴露中國高層黑幕，2月15日在直播中又爆料，共產黨推行的中國夢已經完全不可能實現，<strong><span class=\"red\">今年6月4日「沒有共產黨的新中國一定會成立」，屆時會由世界上許多國家共同宣布。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n6/4成立新中國不是開玩笑？郭文貴宣佈：將發表「建國宣言」 <br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3180135\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3180135&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJCZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=53922823\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3180135&h=c11c30d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3180135</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"small\">2020-05-28 16:19</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2020/05/28/phpNOwInl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2020%2F05%2F28%2FphpNOwInl.jpg&h=a2982b6c&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n<br />\n儘管如今距離6月4日僅剩1週，中共要「準時」倒台的可能性微乎其微，不過郭文貴27日仍聲稱，他將在紐約時間6月3日直播發表「建國宣言」，曾在川普政府任職的前白宮首席策士班農（Steve Bannon）也將參與直播，並一同宣讀該宣言。<br />\n<br />\n另外，<span class=\"red\"><strong>郭文貴曾在去年初的直播發誓「2020年是結束共產黨在中國的最後1年，否則文貴就從那18樓跳下去，大家要記住我的承諾」，不過他在2週前的直播中改口，要大家別當真，笑稱這只是「開玩笑」</strong></span>，要大家輕鬆過日子，強調「我要真幹那事兒，我就不會在鏡頭前說了」、<strong><span class=\"red\">「要不6月4號不行，我裸泳得了」</span></strong>。"},{"pid":"e3165d72487def43a27cf7772d0448a88e54a5e5","tid":2159294,"uid":19217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:33:14.000Z","msg":"大內宣"},{"pid":"12badccb3e3dc78490b808ef45cb65a9df8a0c3b","tid":2159294,"uid":27458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c9422fc77a2972cdcabc8a400277c961637c03","tid":2159294,"uid":7860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"419ece7c481e978cc04cb72aa27bfea9f05cf958","tid":2159294,"uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c10388a6275e7426403e90b8f8a132305d45ee25","tid":2159294,"uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e575353e870bbb972bece35c9daa6fb2ce3c7fd1","tid":2159294,"uid":250888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:52:50.000Z","msg":"點解<br />\n美國本土？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:19:46.000Z","msg":"吹牛吹到連fbi都睇唔過眼要查佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:24:08.000Z","msg":"返你公司總部睇睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ding_gang/status/1294404213041225734?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fding_gang%2Fstatus%2F1294404213041225734%3Fs%3D20&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJCZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=9aa8f9